## Codebase Structure

```
project_root/
├── data/                  # local datasets (large files gitignored)
├── notebooks/             # numbered analytical notebooks
├── output/                # charts (PNG), metadata (JSON), reports (MD/CSV)
├── raw/                   # immutable source materials (papers, downloads, scrapes)
├── wiki/                  # LLM-owned distilled knowledge — index.md, log.md, pages
├── insights/              # evidence-based findings doc + INDEX (project-level)
├── methods/               # methodology notes
├── deliverables/          # external memos, briefings, decks (per-profile templates)
├── plan/                  # multi-phase implementation plans (gitignored)
├── brainstorms/           # decision-rationale write-ups feeding plans (gitignored)
├── scripts/               # build scripts behind notebooks
├── manifest.jsonl         # append-only log of every analytical run (reproducibility ledger)
├── .claude/
│   ├── conventions/       # full convention protocols (read on demand)
│   ├── hooks/             # Stop / PostToolUse / PreCompact nudges
│   ├── skills/            # invokable Anthropic-format skills (slash commands)
│   ├── agents/            # subagents (e.g. forked review fan-out)
│   └── settings.json      # project-shared Claude Code settings
└── CLAUDE.md              # this file
```

